Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
