Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我妹妹给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我的缘故…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  水坂君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为毕业去向的事  去了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟也没有其他要留学的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找老师商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留学？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这与跟柚季关系不好的事无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也没往那方面想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中毕业后就去海外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我们以前还抢过馒头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那家伙做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是故意做给我看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许还是分开生活为好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想让我为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在也无法恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有烟花从湖面升起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季会不会现在也还想看烟花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花什么的  已经是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都约定好了一起去看烟花的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为飞碟而中止了  这也是没办法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请支持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能得到您的支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以看飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要看飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为和飞碟扯上关系不是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  诺艾尔也不要说奇怪的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  外面的那个是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您支持我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以请你停止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给其他顾客添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有给别人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听到顾客抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实小春也是想把我赶走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像在其他地方一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我说出伤人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给各位添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这份传单…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直都是站在柚季这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经  没有可以去的地方了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔会更加更加努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那孩子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂同学那人  到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们住的地方不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要班里的各位共同协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够将飞碟赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂那家伙从初中就这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有这毛病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  椎原同学也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解柚季的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会嘲笑她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不了解她  为什么要这么说她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以不要帮柚季的忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因为柚季的原因  给小春添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你聊一聊  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果是柚季的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来  小春应该更加了解才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能和柚季和好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我应该更了解她才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做  才能够帮到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和柚季谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有人理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果都不想帮我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也不需要他人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做  只会给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春你也是认为店铺更加重要对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么说
